title: Malizia - Salvatore Samperi - DVD
description:
This is a DVD version I found of Malizia, one of the best movies I've seen. I don't like writing plots or reviews. It's an italian comedy with some nudity. Miles away from Hollywood comedies. I'm saying this because this is considered an erotic movie, which is not true at all. Maybe it was, but in 1973.

If you try to read some comments, be careful, some people in imdb and wikipedia write about the ending of the movie. I thank god I don't read any reviews before watching movies otherwise i would be thinking about committing suicide.
